    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic, well-maintained vehicle! It's in good condition and offers a smooth, reliable driving experience that you can count on. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior has been cared for with pride. This is a dependable choice for anyone looking for quality and value!",
